This product is a from-scratch Rust reimplementation of Litestream v0.5
(https://github.com/benbjohnson/litestream), pinned to tag v0.5.11, and of the
LTX file format defined by github.com/superfly/ltx (tag v0.5.1).

Litestream is Copyright (c) Ben Johnson and the Litestream authors, licensed
under the Apache License, Version 2.0. The LTX format and reference
implementation are Copyright (c) Superfly, Inc., licensed under the Apache
License, Version 2.0.

This project ports behavior and test vectors from those works for the purpose
of wire-compatible interoperability (PLAN.md D-1). The upstream sources are
vendored read-only under reference/ for reference and differential testing.
